  "texts": [
    "Starting with simple diagnostic tools the field was soon able to outperform trained pathologists in tumor detection.",
    "Subsequently, research demonstrated that patterns in WSIs can be used for prognostic tasks as well, facilitating therapy decisions based on mutational status, drug response, or overall survival.",
    "Nevertheless, rapid changes in the model landscape of DL make it challenging for companies to develop these technologies into static products.",
    "To put this into perspective, in 2023, only four AI-based tools were FDAapproved and applied in pathology [63].",
    "Therefore, it would be clearly desirable to increase this number and move more DL tools into diagnostic routine in precision oncology."
  ],
